Package: jlcarveth-dev
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd, nginx, ucf
Recommends: ca-certificates
Description: Personal portfolio and blog website
 jlcarveth.dev is a Fresh (Deno) web application serving as John Carveth's
 personal portfolio, showcasing projects and problem-solving skills.
 .
 The application is compiled to a standalone binary using deno compile,
 requiring no Deno runtime on the production system. It is served behind
 an nginx reverse proxy.
